<chapter id="roadmap">
  <title>Roadmap</title>
  <para>
    Roadmap is a list of things to be done, and when they should be done.
  </para>

  <sect1 id="roadmap-2-15-dev">
    <title>2-15 Development</title>
    <para>
      These should be done before the GNOME 2-15 development branch becomes stable.
    </para>
    <informaltable>
      <tgroup cols="2">
        <thead>
          <row>
            <entry>Task</entry>
            <entry>Percent Complete</entry>
          </row>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry>Use the callbacks in libnotify to do a What's this? type help prompt.</entry>
            <entry>20% (needs dep on never libnotify)</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>Give user a choice to abort all actions.</entry>
            <entry>0%</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>Give the user the ability to force an Inhibit()'d action</entry>
            <entry>10% (discussed)</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>Add info and graphs by default.</entry>
            <entry>100%</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>Hide graphs that do not apply</entry>
            <entry>0%</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>Integrate g-p-m with more modules, e.g. nautilus.</entry>
            <entry>40%</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>Improve DBUS interface</entry>
            <entry>90%</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </informaltable>
  </sect1>

</chapter>
